= SDL_RenderDrawRect =
Use this function to draw a rectangle on the current rendering target.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_RenderDrawRect(const SDL_Rect* rect)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''rect'''
|the destination [[SDL_Rect]] structure, or NULL to outline the entire rendering target
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

